91
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:26,540
[Father] Hang onto that rail!
Stay right there!

92
00:14:26,610 --> 00:14:28,380
I'll be back!

93
00:14:34,190 --> 00:14:38,020
Stay there! I'm gonna help these guys!
Don't move! Hang on!

94
00:14:38,090 --> 00:14:42,290
[Passengers Screaming]

95
