- Hey, Alec!

98
00:15:42,190 --> 00:15:43,660
[Alec] Dad!

99
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:48,660
[Father Growling]

100
00:15:53,730 --> 00:15:55,170
Help!

101
00:16:00,570 --> 00:16:02,130
Dad!

102
00:16:33,040 --> 00:16:36,440
