103
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:49,610
Help!

104
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:57,530
[Alec Gasping]

105
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:08,000
[Ship's Horn Blaring]

106
00:17:08,070 --> 00:17:10,370
Help!

107
00:17:14,950 --> 00:17:17,850
Help!

108
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:20,910
- [Gasping]
- [Horse Snorting]

109
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:03,960
