[Whinnying]

115
00:24:13,630 --> 00:24:19,040
[Groaning, Snorts]

116
00:24:20,440 --> 00:24:25,040
[Whinnying]

117
00:25:04,420 --> 00:25:08,910
[Whinnying Loudly]

118
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:52,220
[Thunder Rumbling]

119
00:26:19,590 --> 00:26:23,360
- [Gasps]
- [Thunderclap]

120
