[Whinnying, Stomping]

124
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:44,930
[Whistling]

125
00:34:40,120 --> 00:34:45,990
[Whistling, Smacks Lips]

126
00:34:48,130 --> 00:34:52,400
[Snorting]

127
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:35,340
[Smacks Lips, Whistles]

128
00:35:41,590 --> 00:35:43,180
[Whinnying]

129
00:36:47,550 --> 00:36:50,710
[Whinnying]

130
00:36:50,790 --> 00:36:53,050
